  <brief_title>Feasibility of the Latella Implant System for Medial Osteoarthritis (OA)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Latella Implant System for Lateralization of the Iliotibial Band to Offload the Medial Condyle for Pain Relief in Patients With Medial Osteoarthritis - A Safety Study</official_title>
